title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
